## How to Run\
1.  Download this repository.\
2.  Open `index.html` in any modern web browser (Chrome, Safari, Edge).\
3.  No installation or backend server is required.\
\
## Usage Scenario\
1.  **Navigate** to the "Log" tab.\
2.  **Type** "Oatmeal" or click the **Microphone** icon to simulate voice input.\
3.  Click **Log Data**.\
4.  Observe the **AI Tip** on the Dashboard update based on your input.\
